0-10s视频，播放进度达到99%为有效播放；
10-15秒视频，播放时长达到10秒为有效播放；
15-30秒视频，播放进度达到 (1/3*x+5)/100 为有效播放；
30-60秒视频，播放进度达到 (1/6*x+10)/100 为有效播放；
60-120秒视频，播放进度达到 (2/30*x+16)/100 为有效播放；
120-180秒视频，播放进度达到 (0.05*x+18)/100 为有效播放；
180秒以上视频，播放时长达到27秒为有效播放。"}]

subject: 流量
tabledesc: 记录搜索请求可见点击，每天分区是当天的增量。概述： 搜索宽表gdm_04_search_di，是通过搜索结果页的请求，可见，点击事件进行数据汇总得到。包含可见曝光量，点击曝光量，以及其他数据维度  加工使用的事件： search_newest_list_expo_show search_newest_list_ad_expo_show search_newest_list_sight_show search_newest_list_ad_sight_show search_newest_list_click search_newest_list_ad_click  上游数据表： fdm_flw_app_event_union_di   常用sql逻辑： 1、搜索次数统计 select  count(distinct case when box_type not in ('mtab') then if(a.platform='01',search_id,query_id) end) as search_num    --- 搜索次数 from gdm.gdm_04_search_di a  where dt = '2022-08-23'   and app_key in ('auto_android','auto_iphone')   -- 区分appkey and platform='04'       -- 分端 and search_cate_id='1'  -- 综合频道，这么限制就只查综合频道    2、搜索DAU select  count(distinct case when length(if(platform='01',search_id,query_id))>3 then cookie end)    -- 搜索dau from gdm.gdm_04_search_di a  where dt = '2022-08-23'   and app_key in ('auto_android','auto_iphone')       -- 区分appkey and platform in ('01','02','03')                    -- 分端   3、搜索词数量 select  count(distinct query_keyword)     --- 搜索词数量 from gdm.gdm_04_search_di a  where dt = '2022-08-23'   and app_key in ('auto_android','auto_iphone')       -- 区分appkey and platform in ('01','02','03')                    -- 分端    4、搜索结果页，点击，曝光可见 select sum(case when is_expo=1 then 1 else 0 end) as req_expo_num,    -- 请求曝光量         sum(sight_show_num) as sight_show_num,    -- 可见曝光量         sum(click_num) as click_num,     -- 点击量 from gdm.gdm_04_search_di a  where dt = '2022-08-23'   and app_key in ('auto_android','auto_iphone')       -- 区分appkey and platform in ('01','02','03')                    -- 分端

APP

Android：进入后台（inactive）超过30s则原访次结束，再进入生成新访次，报一条启动日志。杀掉进程（kill）则原访次结束，再进入生成新访次，报一条启动日志

IOS：按home键或杀掉进程都是kill状态，原访次结束，再进入生成新访次，报一条启动日志。

PCM

30分钟没有下一个浏览行为，即pv记录，则访次ID失效，30分钟之后再来时，就会生成一个新的访次ID。

如果30分钟之内产生了下一个pv，则会更新该cookie的有效期，重新设置为30分钟。

由于有效期会在产生pv时进行更新，因此一个访次的最长时间不是30分钟，而是可以足够长。"},{"name":"user_id","index":4,"comment":"注册用户id","type":"string","desc":"用户登录后浏览即可获取其注册用户id，未登录该字段为0"},{"name":"user_name","index":5,"comment":"注册用户名称","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"reg_time","index":6,"comment":"注册时间 ","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"first_login_dt","index":7,"comment":"首次登陆时间","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"last_login_dt","index":8,"comment":"末次登录时间","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"reg_platform","index":9,"comment":"注册平台；01:PC 02:M 03:APP","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"reg_product","index":10,"comment":"注册产品 ","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"sex","index":11,"comment":"用户性别 ","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"user_status","index":12,"comment":"用户状态 ","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"is_bind_mobile","index":13,"comment":"是否绑定手机","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"mobile_province_id","index":14,"comment":"手机号归属省份id  ","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"mobile_city_id","index":15,"comment":"手机号归属城市id  ","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"create_time","index":16,"comment":"创建时间 ","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"start_time","index":17,"comment":"App端开始时间   ","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"end_time","index":18,"comment":"App端结束时间   ","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"first_visit_time","index":19,"comment":"首次访问时间","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"first_visit_dt","index":20,"comment":"用户最早来访时间   ","type":"string","desc":""},{"name":"is_new_user","index":21,"comment":"是否新用户(cookie、设备) ;  1:是 0：否 ","type":"string","desc":"PC、M端为cookie在当前访端首次来访时间是否当天
